<i>adverb</i>: 버젓이 [버저시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>버젓이 [버저시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. brazenly; shamelessly; overtly</dd><br>
<dd>남의 시선을 신경 써서 조심하지 않고 뻔뻔하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being careless and bold-faced without being self-conscious.</dd><br>
<dd>2. decently; presentably</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 뒤지지 않을 정도로 번듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being so respectable as to be second to none.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>